@takluyver Thanks for reviewing and sharing your thoughts. I was thinking to just show either "Pause" or "Resume" button depending on the state of the notebook like a toggle. How do you feel about that ? On persistent notification, I will read more about the clickable notifications in notebook and try to use them here. For testing, I was thinking to run like a print loop and check affects of pause and resume (using selenium).
